{"tid":754230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴表態聲援奧斯爾：我們是多元化球會","createTime":"2018-07-24T08:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T06:45:03.000Z","uid":153600,"like":43,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"789351e951aacb1b711a04f6359c6e8c1a86b508","tid":754230,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:51:44.000Z","msg":"香港時間7月23日，阿仙奴通過社交媒體聲援奧斯爾，並稱阿仙奴是一個多元化的球會。<br />\n<br />\n　　昨日奧斯爾在個人社交網站宣佈退出德國國家隊，將不再為國家隊效力。奧斯爾聲稱自己遭遇了種族歧視和不尊重，而德國足協主席萊因哈德-格連德爾對他的不公待遇也讓他寒心。<br />\n<br />\n　　在奧斯爾發佈了退出國家隊的聲明後，德國足協在今日早些時間也發佈聲明。在聲明中，德國足協感謝了奧斯爾對德國足球所做出的貢獻，並尊重奧斯爾的決定；但對於奧斯爾提到的種族歧視一事，德國足協表示不存在。<br />\n<br />\n         而阿仙奴在社交媒體上也發佈了動態，表達了對奧斯爾的支持。官推上寫道：「我們的多元化是阿仙奴球會如此獨一無二的原因。在一起。阿仙奴隊內的每一個人。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/9060550/6/20180724?cf=fb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.soccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F9060550%2F6%2F20180724%3Fcf%3Dfb&d=dvfv8g2v7mlOHxVCz%2Bi7utU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6a4367d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.soccer.sina.com.hk/news/article/9060550/6/20180724?cf=fb</a>"},{"pid":"18e66e2d074a5d6a623ec775258199e23bffea94","tid":754230,"uid":43328,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:32:52.000Z","msg":"班妓屌佢既次數分分鐘多過德國班友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c506a8cf867ae9aa703247e049587bc39d75fe41","tid":754230,"uid":139873,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d344bbf20f96073ff34c076b912c791bd01e20a","tid":754230,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee12d449362ece344ce0473a3b8a9447d27cb15","tid":754230,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{